,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:28:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影景Sony or Nikon only <br />\n<br />\na6000+sel1018</blockquote><br />\n有冇話邊部會適合新手多D? <br />\n唔該巴打!"},{"pid":"e5ad447f71a28326a069272fcf6fbe62905fa9b3","tid":380230,"uid":134163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T04:01:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>0經驗<br />\n想學影景多<br />\nBudget 10-12k<br />\n求推介 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我也是新手,都想知影景如果想用wide鏡頭影景,用那款機(如Nikon,Sony,Canon)會容易配到些平靚正(一般人會用)的選擇,要預多多少錢來買? 如果容易影到夜景更好(旅行時用)."},{"pid":"32574ade5e0c060657c92b8756e6a581c5e5006e","tid":380230,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>影景Sony or Nikon only <br />\n<br />\na6000+sel1018</blockquote><br />\n有冇話邊部會適合新手多D? <br />\n唔該巴打!</blockquote><br />\n買機買硬淨加功能好就得<br />\n用傻瓜Mode難學野"},{"pid":"df4acab2d3a5beeef87fea7d540620b2844b00a0","tid":380230,"uid":120101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T04:07:14.000Z","msg":"用電話練好基本功先"},{"pid":"0815c87448a059726af1492c84143d1408ee4101","tid":380230,"uid":13808,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T04:08:24.000Z","msg":"12k剩機定連鏡"},{"pid":"64997bb2bfd0e74489ae7ce5b87a65734dafa618","tid":380230,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T04:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用電話練好基本功先</blockquote><br />\nNSDAP?"},{"pid":"07632da6ea035cab886417e97c5475e67b2dc196","tid":380230,"uid":78755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:51:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手咁快就10-12k<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你係唔係肯定長玩</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n人地12k當散紙唔得咩，理人咁多"},{"pid":"ec7fcab4724955f80a254ce1d6656b2b3030b574","tid":380230,"uid":12302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:28:03.000Z","msg"