\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上依家新入職, 唔算太多野做, 想發展下新興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位巴打比既意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9c93fd8cb6283c96daf85177fc20b97d92d1ff","tid":380230,"uid":1818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:51:12.000Z","msg":"a7ii kit<br />\n之後再儲錢買鏡"},{"pid":"745abc1d5a4dbd0aa1e08c3612c4574b07b4f861","tid":380230,"uid":9160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:53:26.000Z","msg":"賣部10d比你<br />\n250,好抵玩"},{"pid":"3328e32836152116e6e45f809caf11fe6a398b7d","tid":380230,"uid":173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:51:48.000Z","msg":"點睇eos 800D?"},{"pid":"75967b2536f09d5fe71644aab740389c1ca59e6b","tid":380230,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:54:58.000Z","msg":"fujifilm xt2"},{"pid":"85b536ccb135982c2e5d358c5820de4d3eabfc9c","tid":380230,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T23:03:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}